<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the Zend_Db_Table_Rowset_Abstract on line 119 there is the following line:</p>

<p>@Zend_Loader::loadClass($this-&gt;_rowClass);</p>

<p>This will load the class file for the defined rowClass. However if the defined class has errors, those errors will be supressed by the @ in the Zend_Loader line. So you won't have any idea what is going on, because the errors aren't reported anywhere.</p>

